Build audience profiles that you can use anywhere.












What is Adobe Audience Manager?



 






































See what Audience Manager can do.
















360-degree profiles
Audience activation
Cross-device measurement
Look-alike modeling
…









Combine information from online, offline and second- and third-party sources to create complete audience profiles.

 













Conveniently target specific profiles on any content delivery platform, like content management systems and ad servers.

 













Identify, measure and target people as they move across screens and devices.

 













Identify prospects who are similar in behavior to your most valuable customers, so you can extend your reach.

 


















 



 








 
 
















 
We’re a leader in data management platforms. Forrester agrees.



 















